           PaneBox[
            
            StyleBox["\<\"HypExpand[HypSeries, ParSub, VarSub, {Eps, Ord}, \
NPrec, opts] numerically expands a hypergeometric series HypSeries around \
Eps=0 up to order Ord with NPrec correct digits.\\nHypSeries is a \
hypergeometric series given in terms of Pochhammer functions.\\nParSub is the \
list of substitution rules for the Pochhammer parameters:\\n  \[Bullet] {a \
\[Rule] 1+\[Epsilon], b \[Rule] 1/2, c \[Rule] 2-\[Epsilon], ...}\\nVarSub is \
the list of substitution rules for the kinematic variables, specifying the \
evaluation point:\\n  \[Bullet] {x \[Rule] 1/5, y \[Rule] 1/4, ...}\\nThe \
result is the list of Laurent coefficients from the lowest non-vanishing \
order to Ord.\\nOptions:\\n  \[Bullet] IDelta      (default: -I)    \
\[LongDash] infinitesimal imaginary shift\\n  \[Bullet] VerboseMode (default: \
False) \[LongDash] print progress information\\n  \[Bullet] ParallelRun \
(default: True)  \[LongDash] use parallel evaluation\\nExamples:\\n  \
HypExpand[Pochhammer[a,m+n] Pochhammer[b1,m] Pochhammer[b2,n] / \
(Pochhammer[c,m+n] m! n!) x^m y^n,\\n            {a \[Rule] 1, b1 \[Rule] \
1/2, b2 \[Rule] 1/3, c \[Rule] 2}, {x \[Rule] 1/5, y \[Rule] 1/4}, \
{\[Epsilon], 2}, 50]\"\>", "InformationUsageText",
