AppellF4[a, b, c1, c2, x, y]                  -- coincides with LauricellaFC \
at n=2\n\n  Horn G- and H-series (2 variables, defined within HyperPrecision; \
   use ?HornG1, ?HornH1, etc. to see the series definition and call \
signature):\n  \[Bullet] HornG1, HornG2, HornG3\n  \[Bullet] HornH1, HornH2, \
HornH3, HornH4, HornH5, HornH6, HornH7\n\n  Lauricella series (n variables, \
