    "CheckIntegrability[PfaffianIN, Vars] checks the Frobenius integrability \
conditions d_j M_i - d_i M_j + [M_i, M_j] = 0 for every pair of variables in \
Vars.\nPfaffianIN is the Pfaffian system (4-tuple) returned by \
FindPfaffianSystem[] or FindPfaffianSystemBasis[]; the connection matrices \
M_i are taken from it.\nVars is the list of kinematic variables:\n  \[Bullet] \
{x, y, ...}\nThe check is performed numerically at a randomly chosen rational \
point. Prints PASSED or FAILED for each pair, and returns True if all pairs \
pass, False otherwise.\nExamples:\n  CheckIntegrability[PfaffianSystemIN, {x, \
y}]", "Documentation" -> None, "OwnValues" -> None, "UpValues" -> None, 
    "DownValues" -> 
    Information`InformationValueForm[
     DownValues, HyperPrecision`CheckIntegrability, {
      HyperPrecision`CheckIntegrability[
         Pattern[HyperPrecision`Private`pfaffianRaw, 
          Blank[]], 
         Pattern[HyperPrecision`Private`vars, 
          Blank[List]]] :> 
       Module[{HyperPrecision`Private`pairs, HyperPrecision`Private`pfaffian, 
          HyperPrecision`Private`AllPair}, 
         If[Length[HyperPrecision`Private`vars] === 1, 
           HyperPrecision`Private`AllPair = {True}, 
           HyperPrecision`Private`pairs = 
            Subsets[HyperPrecision`Private`vars, {2}]; 
           HyperPrecision`Private`pfaffian = 
            Part[HyperPrecision`Private`pfaffianRaw, 3]; 
           HyperPrecision`Private`AllPair = 
            Map[HyperPrecision`Private`IntegrabilityCheckNum[
               HyperPrecision`Private`pfaffian[
                Part[#, 1]], 
               HyperPrecision`Private`pfaffian[
                Part[#, 2]], 
               Part[#, 1], 
               Part[#, 2]]& , HyperPrecision`Private`pairs]; Null]; If[
           Apply[And, HyperPrecision`Private`AllPair], 
           Print["PASSED!!"], 
           Print["FAILED!!"]]; Return[
           Apply[And, HyperPrecision`Private`AllPair]]]}], "SubValues" -> 
    None, "DefaultValues" -> None, "NValues" -> None, "FormatValues" -> None, 
    "Options" -> None, "Attributes" -> {}, "FullName" -> 
